(D) Coinffeine Company decides to no longer provide the Coinffeine Software or 
certain parts of the Coinffeine Software to users in the country in which you 
are resident or from which you use the service, or the provision of the 
Coinffeine Software or certain Coinffeine Software services to you by 
Coinffeine Company is, in Coinffeine Company's sole discretion, no longer 
commercially viable.

